WEBVTT

00:14:59.906 --> 00:15:01.658
toward the other,

00:15:01.682 --> 00:15:04.927
and to do something or try to do something

00:15:04.951 --> 00:15:08.073
other than rejection or attack.

00:15:08.545 --> 00:15:10.711
We can do this with our siblings

00:15:10.735 --> 00:15:12.137
and our mates

00:15:12.161 --> 00:15:14.417
and our friends and our colleagues.

00:15:14.441 --> 00:15:17.069
We can do this with the disconnection

00:15:17.093 --> 00:15:19.843
and the discord all around us.

00:15:20.410 --> 00:15:24.076
We can do this for the soul of the world.

00:15:24.629 --> 00:15:25.820
Thank you.

00:15:25.844 --> 00:15:31.840
(Applause)